{"tid":1030262,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡海軍命名方法好有皇家海軍味道","createTime":"2019-02-20T23:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T23:22:02.000Z","uid":238189,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7501cb567873b842e130355b45264aa4052f43a9","tid":1030262,"uid":238189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:29:09.000Z","msg":"勝利級導彈護衛艦（英語：Victory-Class Missile Corvette）是新加坡共和國海軍的多用途船隻，由新加坡引進德國呂森造船廠（英語：L&uuml;rssen）的MGB 62型設計方案建造而成[1]。勝利級共建造六艘，分別於1990年至1991年投入服役並編入新加坡海軍的188中隊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/21/072014_35308254444e3619a5498d08472d018e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F21%2F072014_35308254444e3619a5498d08472d018e.png&h=9f5c678e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼承英國皇家海軍傳統，船隻命名型得黎又唔老土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲要全部首字母相同玩食字。<br />\n<br />\n真係好酸佢地作為獨立國家有能力組織軍隊可以掌握自己命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a558fe5ccbaf9d1f0ebbd2e359a73a16ef7fcca","tid":1030262,"uid":238189,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:33:22.000Z","msg":"可畏級多功能隱形護衛艦<br />\nRSS 可畏號Formidable（68）&mdash; 2007年服役<br />\nRSS 無畏號Intrepid（69）&mdash; 2008年服役<br />\nRSS 堅定號Steadfast（70）&mdash; 2008年服役<br />\nRSS 頑強號Tenacious（71）&mdash; 2008年服役<br />\nRSS 堅韌號Stalwart（72）&mdash; 2009年服役<br />\nRSS 無上號Supreme（73）&mdash; 2009年服役<br />\n<br />\n獨立級近海任務艦<br />\nRSS 獨立號Independence（15）&mdash; 2016年服役<br />\nRSS 主權號Sovereignty（16）&mdash; 2017年服役<br />\nRSS 統一號Unity（17）&mdash; 2017年服役<br />\nRSS Justice (18) &mdash; 2018年服役<br />\nRSS Indomitable (19) &mdash; 2018年服役<br />\n<br />\n無畏級巡邏艇<br />\nRSS 勇氣號Brave（95）&mdash; 1995年服役<br />\nRSS 英勇號Gallant（97）&mdash;1997年服役<br />\nRSS 不屈號Dauntless（99）&mdash; 1997年服役<br />\nRSS 自由號Freedom（86）&mdash; 1998年服役<br />\n<br />\n挑戰者級（Challenger class 原名為索羅門級，Sj&ouml;ormen class）潛艇<br />\nRSS 挑戰者號&mdash; 1997年服役，2015年退役<br />\nRSS 征服者號&mdash; 1999年服役<br />\nRSS 百夫長號&mdash; 1999年服役，2015年退役<br />\nRSS 酋長號&mdash; 2001年服役<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2249e1c176e491150f8d573e1c2fcc3eddddc27f","tid":1030262,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"541eb7112e277fb1dd0f771f430e0e48b597809f","tid":1030262,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:34:30.000Z","msg":"型能到..."},{"pid":"2a8a7eb54c183af6fcbc3db18150c15f645628b1","tid":1030262,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:36:04.000Z","msg":"見到勝利級諗起蘇俄d潛艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e83a6901882a3fcbb7ec533ec16468c90ceffda","tid":1030262,"uid":238189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2249e1c176e491150f8d573e1c2fcc3eddddc27f","tid":1030262,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T23:49:53.000Z","msg":"英國佬應該真係有可能以此命名，二戰就有艘V級驅逐艦叫Virago(潑婦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a74573f6c3ea7e1c899f9081a3c2fb17fc695d","tid":1030262,"uid":4596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T00:00:48.000Z","msg":"希望有一日會見到Warspite<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者就咁叫Dreadnought都已經J撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647d11573ca85e6127323a51376b3de54518811b","tid":1030262,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e83a6901882a3fcbb7ec533ec16468c90ceffda","tid":1030262,"uid":238189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2249e1c176e491150f8d573e1c2fcc3eddddc27f","tid":1030262,"uid":5032